igation bar by removing the checkmark next to "Show in menus."<br/><br/>You can remove your site from being listed in search results by removing the checkmark next to "Show in search." <br/><br/>After you have made these changes, hit the "Save" button in the bottom right hand of the editing pane.<br/><br/>[Screenshot]</p>\n<h3>Deleting Pages</h3>\n<h3/>', 'Managing Your Site', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, 0, 3, NULL, 0, 0, 'Saved (update)', NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', NULL, 5, '0.9'),
